<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If you have a Zend_Date object $date with an internal date of
2009-12-28 00:00:00
and you perform
$date-&gt;addWeek(1)-&gt;subMinute(1)
the result is
2009-01-03 23:59:00.</p>

<p>Shouldn't this be 2010-01-03 23:59:00?</p>

